    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The `change` is the way to go. The fact that  URL updates when the searchbox is used with the options `searchOnEnterKeyPress` is not nice but that's better that any of the bugs introduced with using `search` instead of the `change` event.",
